    "body": "I may have misspoke on it being a precompile in gitter, it's just a shortcut to that finalized ERC layout. I agree with above about how it's good to have these sorts of built in types available, but ERC20 does have some optional components and that makes this shortcut a little prescriptive. Something to think about moving forward.\r\n\r\nI agree on the different syntax piece, it should be more standardized.",
